Job Responsibilities:

  Preparation of all menu items in accordance
  Daily preparation of ingredients and menu items
  Responsible with the opening and closing of restaurant kitchen
  Assist in providing high level of food standards and customer service to customers
  Maintain an enthusiastic and energetic approach to enhancing experience, responding to and communicating with crew.
  Respond to and communicate effectively with other crew members and management.

Job Requirements:

  Candidate must possess at least a Primary/Secondary School/"O" Level, any field.
  At least 1 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.
  Able to work on weekends and public holidays.
